params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\", 'FM999990') as \\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\", " +" B1.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" B1.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY, " +" M_WH B1, " +" M_WH B2, " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.WH_CD = B1.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM_RCV_WH.ITEM_CD(+) " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.PLANT_CD = M_ITEM_RCV_WH.PLANT_CD(+) " +" and M_ITEM_RCV_WH.WH_CD = B2.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\""

"update " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"set " +" \\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"insert into " +" M_WH_PRIORITY(\\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?))"
"delete from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" = ? " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" as \\"WH_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\", 'FM999990') as \\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\", " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" as \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\" " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?)"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.\\"WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"for update nowait"
"insert into " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH(\\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"WH_CD\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?)"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH.WH_CD, " +" M_WH.WH_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH, " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD(+) " +" AND M_ITEM_RCV_WH.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_RCV_WH.PLANT_CD = ?"
"UPDATE " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH " +"SET " +" WH_CD = ? " +"WHERE " +" ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ?"
"DELETE FROM " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_RCV_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" MRP_FLG, " +" PLANT_CD " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" WH_CD = ?"
"select " +" WH_CD " +"from " +" m_wh " +"where " +" wh_cd = ? " +" and plant_cd = ? " +" and MRP_FLG <> 1"
"SELECT " +" WH_CD " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM_RCV_WH " +"WHERE " +" ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND PLANT_CD = ? " +"for update nowait"
